54:17.321 --> 54:18.522
I'm Judy Woodruff.

54:18.522 --> 54:20.991
GWEN IFILL: And I'm Gwen Ifill.

54:20.991 --> 54:24.661
Join us online and again here
tomorrow evening. For all of us
here at the "PBS NewsHour,"

54:24.661 --> 54:25.062
thank you, and good night.

